OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT beasthunter       ~%kitid%~
OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT fireweapon        ~%s1%~
OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT quicksilver       ~%s2%~
OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT holysymbolhunter  ~%m9%~


